OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FWords by Emily Youlton, Senior
OL,7,FPolitics Producer
OL,9,FAndy Burnham has set out his plans to
OL,10,F"fix politics" as he promised to "do
OL,11,Fthings differently" in his first
OL,12,Fpolicy speech.
OL,14,FHe still looks poised to succeed Sir
OL,15,FKeir Starmer following his resignation
OL,16,Fas prime minister after continued
OL,17,Fpressure from the Labour Party
OL,18,Ffollowing disastrous local election
OL,19,Fresults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
