FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FThe former Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fwon a crucial by-election in
OL,8,FMakerfield, which had been triggered
OL,9,Fwith the sole purpose of allowing him
OL,10,Fto run for the leadership as a sitting
OL,11,Fmember of parliament.
OL,13,FIn his first major speech, the 'King
OL,14,Fof the North' has now explained some
OL,15,Fideas for how he would lead the Labour
OL,16,FParty and the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FAs the UK has a parliamentary
OL,7,Fdemocracy, there will not be a general
OL,8,Felection just because there's a new
OL,9,Fprime minister and some opposition
OL,10,Fhave warned that if Burnham steers too
OL,11,Ffar away from the manifesto that
OL,12,FLabour were elected on, then he'd face
OL,13,Fincreasing pressure to do something.
OL,15,FSpeaking in Manchester, he set out his
OL,16,Fideas for a "Number 10 of the North"
OL,17,Fand plans for increased devolution to
OL,18,Freallocate spending to local
OL,19,Fauthorities and mayors to make the
OL,20,Fdecisions locally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FBurnham did not take questions from
OL,7,Fjournalists following his speech, a
OL,8,Fdecision criticised by many reporters
OL,9,Fas a way of avoiding scrutiny.
OL,11,FHere ITV News looks at the first of
OL,12,FBurnham's ideas and how it might
OL,13,Fimpact the UK.
OL,15,FNo 10 of the North
OL,17,FBurnham has always been clear that he
OL,18,Fsupports greater devolution of power
OL,19,Fout of Westminster and into regions,
OL,20,Fand today he's said he will create a
OL,21,F"Number 10 of the North".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FThe purpose of creating this
OL,7,FManchester-based operation will be to
OL,8,Ffocus on making "power flow" into all
OL,9,Fregions, including London, and he
OL,10,Fcalled it "the nerve centre for a
OL,11,Frewired Britain".
OL,13,FHe said: "The job of No 10 North will
OL,14,Fbe to make power flow into the
OL,15,FMidlands, into the South West, into
OL,16,Fthe East of England and, yes, into
OL,17,FLondon as I said before, as much as
OL,18,Fthe North East, Yorkshire & the Humber
OL,19,Fand here in the North West."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FHe claimed that the "the whole country
OL,7,Fsuffers when the regions and nations
OL,8,Fare not meeting their potential" and
OL,9,Fpromises that this move of power out
OL,10,Fof London will help to tackle this
OL,11,Fchallenge.
OL,13,FBurnham said there was a disconnect
OL,14,Fwith the civil service in Whitehall
OL,15,Fand said he was "worried" by what he
OL,16,Ffound when in Westminster and wants to
OL,17,F"bring about the biggest rebalancing
OL,18,Fof power our country has seen".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FHe said: "It is time for Whitehall to
OL,7,Faccept that growth cannot be ordered
OL,8,Ffrom the top down. Instead, it can
OL,9,Fonly be nurtured from the bottom up."
OL,11,FIt is not a shock that Burnham
OL,12,Fmentioned housing today, it's an issue
OL,13,Fhe has campaigned on before and was
OL,14,Fvery likely to be included in his
OL,15,Fpolicies.
OL,17,FHe suggested reforms to public housing
OL,18,Fstock citing the loss of "almost 1.5
OL,19,Fmillion council homes since the 1980s".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FHis solution is for his new northern
OL,7,Fbureau of No10 to "oversee the biggest
OL,8,Fcouncil house building programme since
OL,9,Fthe post-war period. We will use
OL,10,Fpublic land, vacant public land to
OL,11,Freduce costs".
OL,13,FHe referenced the Finnish philosophy
OL,14,Fof "Housing First" saying "if you
OL,15,Fdon't give people a good home, what
OL,16,Fchance have they got of having a good
OL,17,Flife?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FBurnham believes that with good and
OL,7,Fstable homes, people rely less on
OL,8,Fhealth services and children can have
OL,9,Fa better education.
OL,11,FPublic Control
OL,13,FThe former mayor has long championed
OL,14,Frenationalisation and public ownership
OL,15,Fof essentials like transport and
OL,16,Fenergy and repeated these calls today.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FHe said: "We will ensure all parts of
OL,7,Fthe UK are able to take greater public
OL,8,Fcontrol of essential services like
OL,9,Fwater, housing, energy and transport,
OL,10,Flearning from the model of that has
OL,11,Ftransformed our bus networks here in
OL,12,FGreater Manchester."
OL,14,FHe has promised a 10-year plan to
OL,15,Freduce the costs of these essentials,
OL,16,Fbut the details of this plan were not
OL,17,Ffully explained.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FAs the Mayor of Manchester, Burnham
OL,7,Fcreated the Bee network, an arms
OL,8,Flength private company with public
OL,9,Foversight, that has seen a joined up
OL,10,Fapproach to the city's transport
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FYoung People
OL,15,FBurnham has seen success with policies
OL,16,Fbenefitting young people in Manchester
OL,17,Flike free bus passes for under-18s and
OL,18,Fhas previously suggested he'd like
OL,19,Fthis to be more nationwide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FOn Monday, he also called for
OL,7,Feducation reform, saying: "We need a
OL,8,Fcomplete rethink of how we support the
OL,9,Fnext generation to succeed."
OL,11,FHe called for an end to a focus on
OL,12,F"the university route" and said focus
OL,13,Fshould also be on "kids who want
OL,14,Fsomething different".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FBurnham is supportive of policies like
OL,7,Fthe 45 day work placement designed to
OL,8,Fhelp tackle the current youth
OL,9,Funemployment crisis. He also said that
OL,10,Fthere needs to be mental health
OL,11,Fsupport provided in work for young
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FBurnham has already held talks with
OL,15,FAlan Milburn, who is currently
OL,16,Fconducting a review into the topic of
OL,17,Fyouth employment and has already found
OL,18,Fthat there are over one million young
OL,19,Fpeople not in employment, education or
OL,20,Ftraining (Neet).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FCost of Living
OL,8,FAlthough not a main feature of the
OL,9,Fpolicies he's announced, Burnham
OL,10,Frepeated statements he made while
OL,11,Fcampaigning in Makerfield about people
OL,12,Fneeding "a bit extra now to help with
OL,13,Frising costs".
OL,15,FHe promised to not take "risks with
OL,16,Fthe public finances" to deliver this,
OL,17,Fbut it is not yet clear what he will
OL,18,Fdo to "give Britain some breathing
OL,19,Fspace" when it comes to the cost of
OL,20,Fliving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FLocal voices championed
OL,8,FA bold promise of "good growth in
OL,9,Fevery postcode" was a focus of the
OL,10,Fspeech, where Burnham is trying to
OL,11,Fappeal to the whole country,
OL,12,Fespecially those outside of his native
OL,13,FManchester.
OL,15,FThe 'King of the North' needed to show
OL,16,Fthat he plans to improve things across
OL,17,Fthe country and his No 10 of the North
OL,18,Fwon't just be focusing on that area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FHe wants to continue devolution plans,
OL,7,Fanswering "the call from Mayors" about
OL,8,Fdevolution of employment support and
OL,9,Fextending powers in the nations of
OL,10,FScotland, Northern Ireland and Wales.
OL,12,FChanges to parliament
OL,14,FBurnham also has plans to change
OL,15,Fparliament aimed at enabling MPs to
OL,16,Frepresent their constiuency interests
OL,17,Fin a better way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FHe proposed the removal of the
OL,7,Fwhipping system, which is where
OL,8,Fparties push their MPs to vote in line
OL,9,Fwith their policy or face penalties
OL,10,Flike removal from the party.
OL,12,FRecently, Labour suspended the whips
OL,13,Ffrom MPs who voted against their
OL,14,Fproposed welfare reforms, which
OL,15,Feventually led to a revolt and the
OL,16,Fgovernment backing down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FBut with questions over whether
OL,7,Fremoving the whip would let MPs vote
OL,8,Fwith the best intention or just make
OL,9,Fhis party ungovernable, this policy
OL,10,Fmade be hard to put into practice.
OL,12,FBurnham has promised reform of
OL,13,Fbusiness rates to try and revive high
OL,14,Fstreets and support pubs, and he
OL,15,Ftalked about the social benefits of
OL,16,Fbusy high streets, and does not want
OL,17,Fthem to become a "marker of decline".
OL,19,FAlthough he said he would cut business
OL,20,Frates, it is not clear yet the funding
OL,21,Fmodel behind it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FHe also said that the UK was
OL,7,Finnovative and promised to "back our
OL,8,Fscientists, technologists,
OL,9,Fentrepreneurs and creatives" as well
OL,10,Fas supporting regions to set "clear
OL,11,Fand credible industrial ambitions".
OL,13,FHe also pledged to change the "UK
OL,14,Fpublic procurement policy" saying that
OL,15,Fhe wants to help "British-based
OL,16,Fsuppliers become more stable and
OL,17,Fcompetitive".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782778699
OL,3,CHow is Andy Burnham planning to 'fix
OL,4,Cpolitics'?
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt seems that Burnham has set out his
OL,12,Fvision for "Manchesterism", where
OL,13,Flocal economies grow creating an
OL,14,Foverall economic benefit for the
OL,15,Fcountry, but it is unclear yet on all
OL,16,Fthe details of how he will actually
OL,17,Fmake it happen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
